sub_title:
Content Writer and Translator in One.
I manage and produce online collateral for ad campaigns. I also translate between English, Russian, and French.
summary: I'm a recent masters' program graduate with a degree in linguistics and communication looking to apply my previous work experience in logistics and multicultural environments to add value to a larger team.
